name: Dr Distorto
details:
Distortion with built in noise gateWith the new Line 6 Dr. Distorto effects pedal, you can achieve singing lead tones with incredible sustain at any distortion level. Dr. Distorto delivers full-bodied distortion tones and features an innovative harmonic feedback circuit and a built-in selectable noise gate.
